# Connect3Game

Connect3Game is a simple and entertaining Android game that combines elements of Tic-Tac-Toe and Connect Four. The objective is to connect three of your game pieces in a row, column, or diagonal while preventing your opponent from achieving the same.

## Features

- Enjoyable gameplay with a twist on classic games.
- Two-player mode: Challenge your friends or family.
- User-friendly interface and interactive design.
- An ideal way to pass the time and have fun on your Android device.

## How to Play

1. Install the game on your Android device.
2. Launch the game and select 'Play' to begin.
3. Take turns with your opponent, aiming to connect three of your pieces.
4. The player who successfully connects three in a row, column, or diagonal wins.

